metadata.description:
Decided to take on a new approach when it comes to making music! I wanted to leave it up to the people. I decided I would make little hooks and post them on TIKTOK and which ever one gained the most traction, I would finish it. 

'Talking' reached 700k views and from that point on I knew I had to finish it!

I got my boy Mark Evans to take this idea and make it come to life and now I feel like its going to be one of those ones that changes my life!
metadata.name: Talking #1
